                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3>Meghalay's society of the Khasi Culture</h3>
                    In Khasi society, women hold power, inherit property, and lead households. Vibrant dances like
                    Nongkrem, celebrating fertility, and Shad Masken, showcasing warrior spirit, reflect their
                    strength and cultural richness.Unlike most societies, Khasi women hold the reins of power. 
                    They inherit ancestral property, make crucial decisions concerning the family and household,
                    and even lead villages and hold political positions.
                </div>    
            </div>
            <br/>
