                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3>Tibet's Vibrant Culture</h3>
                    Tibetan culture is a vibrant tapestry woven from the threads of its unique geography, rich
                    history, and deep spirituality. Nestled high in the Himalayas, Tibet has fostered a
                    distinct way of life for centuries.  Majestic monasteries like Potala Palace and Jokhang Temple
                    stand as testaments to Tibetan architectural prowess. Their colorful facades, intricate
                    carvings, and golden roofs showcase a unique blend of Indian and Chinese influences.
                </div>    
